texts.name: observation_return_one.mp3
texts.text: What a boring trip. At least we got out of our base.

texts.name: observation_return_two.mp3
texts.text: It was good to introduce our selves to the local people, now they know that we are protecting them.

texts.name: observation_return_three.mp3
texts.text: Protecting them from what. There is no bullet been fired for days.

texts.name: observation_return_four.mp3
texts.text: We need to establish a connection to the population, they didn’t trust us and the AAF forces wasn’t a real help. They seemed to be frightened by them. I only saw old people and children out there, seems like a whole generation of inhabitants is missing.

texts.name: observation_return_six.mp3
texts.text: Yeah but where are they now?

texts.name: observation_return_seven.mp3
texts.text: Not a problem to me, as long it keeps quiet on the island, our job is done.
